</strong><strong>Faktor eksternal perubahan sosial : brainly.co.id/tugas/9483387</strong><p><strong>-------------</strong></p><p><strong>ೕ Detail Jawaban ೄྀ࿐</strong></p><strong>Mapel : Sosiologi
